snippet.title: Non Mirage Truth Vision
snippet.description:
» Non Mirage Truth Vision is an American grassroots media outlet offering news, interviews, information, speeches, & much more. Non Mirage Tv promotes a constitutional government, sound money, non-interventionist foreign policy, individual liberty, anti-supremacy, space exploration & clean energy. Material may be uncensored, viewer discretion is advised. For a more convenient viewing experience no videos will be monetized, unless copyright holders choose otherwise. Video uploads are limited. Please watch the 'Liked Playlist' for a consistent flow of news and updates. Non Mirage Tv is non-profit, donations are not accepted. «
Research, stay informed, thanks for watching!
